00:27:12,250 --> 00:27:12,980
No.

503
00:27:13,010 --> 00:27:13,830
Sorry, then.

504
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:14,780
You can't come in.

505
00:27:14,780 --> 00:27:16,500
Sir, I'm a police officer.

506
00:27:16,530 --> 00:27:18,470
