00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,590
I'll say it one last time.

523
00:27:43,610 --> 00:27:45,840
Anthrax is a highly infectious virus.

524
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:47,180
One more minute,

525
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:49,090
