528
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:52,570
Open the door now.

529
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:54,790
Wait a minute.

530
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:56,110
I'll go get the key.

531
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:58,640
